                    <h1>Welcome to PIQuoteDirect</h1>
                                         

                     <p>If your business gives advice or offers a professional service to other businesses you will probably need professional Indemnity insurance. It covers if you are negligent or make a mistake which causes a client's business to suffer financial loss.</p>

 
<p>The types of business that often take out professional indemnity policies include accountants, IT consultants,  architects,  engineers and many more.</p>


  <p>We arrange policies through all major UK insurers and Lloyds of London to provide you with a suitable, comprehensive policy at a competitive price tailor made to your individual requirements.</p>

